2. IMPLEMENTATION SUMMARY
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  LogFeatureEngineer:    5-min windows; LogFeatureVector (errorRate, uniqueTemplateRatio, eventRate,
                         p99Latency, errorBurstScore, newTemplateRate, traceSpanRatio, exceptionRate, totalEvents)
  AnomalyDetectorModel:  Smile IsolationForest.fit(matrix); score(vector), isAnomalous(vector, threshold);
                         serializeModel/loadModel (ObjectOutputStream); AnomalyConfig @Bean with num-trees, subsample-size
  AnomalyEpisodeBuilder: MERGE_GAP 10 min; buildEpisodes(snapshotId, serviceName, vectors, model, threshold);
                         AnomalyEpisode (episodeId, snapshotId, serviceName, startTime, endTime, severity, peakScore, windows, topAnomalousTemplates, summary);
                         AnomalySeverity LOW/MEDIUM/HIGH/CRITICAL by score bands
  AnomalyDetectionService: fetchLogEvents from runtime-events (batch_id, service_name); extractFeatures; train per-service model;
                         buildEpisodes; putObject model-artifacts/anomaly/{snapshotId}/{service}.smile; bulkIndex anomaly-episodes;
                         putJson evidence/anomaly-report/{snapshotId}.json; meter flowforge.anomaly.episodes.detected

